build a library that prints label(representation of record) on Invitation cover.

given list of records in a file.
input format:-
firstName,lastName,gender,age,city,state,country

Output:-
a. Mr/Ms First Last,Country_name,age
b. Mr/Ms Last, First,country_name,age
prefix
male - Mr
female - Ms

age
    legal if > 20
    illegal if < 20
-------------------------------------------------------------

$ cat records.csv
Manisha, Roy, Female, 19, Kolkata, WB, India
Ranju, Karmakar, Male, 22, Bangalore, Karnataka, India

$ sh run.sh informalPrintLabel records.csv India 20
Mr Ranju Karmakar,India,22


recognising Guest as an entity :
firstName,lastName,gender,age,city,state,country

Reading guest records from the file
getting guest labels
